NOTICE — vendored third-party application

apps/studio is a vendored copy of "Open Studio for Strands Agent"
(strands_studio_ui) by xiehust:

    upstream:  https://github.com/xiehust/strands_studio_ui
    commit:    d56f396c16815bb8983210977598c7973746675f
    vendored:  2026-07-09

The upstream repository does not declare an explicit OSS license file at the
vendored commit. It is included here, with attribution, as part of the
AgentCore Launchpad sample asset with the upstream author's repository made
publicly available for this purpose. If the upstream project later adds a
license, that license governs this directory.

Launchpad-specific modifications are intentionally minimal and documented in
docs/studio-integration.md:
  - src/lib/launchpad-client.ts (new): deploy-to-Launchpad API client
  - src/components/launchpad-deploy-section.tsx (new): "Deploy via Launchpad"
    UI section, mounted from agentcore-deploy-panel.tsx
  - src/components/agentcore-deploy-panel.tsx: mounts the section above
  - src/components/main-layout.tsx: "← Launchpad" navigation link
  - vite.config.ts: studio backend proxy → :8100, /launchpad-api → :8000
  - upstream binary screenshots (assets/*.png) removed to keep the repo lean
